article_title: Humana Will Yank Obamacare Plans Serving 100,000 Patients

article_metadata.description: Humana (HUM) said it will discontinue several products offered on government-run exchanges under the Affordable Care Act, impacting about 100,000 individuals currently covered by the insurer's plans across the country.
